- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper's focus on improving the performance of deep learning models in NLP tasks falls under the scope of AI research. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper discusses the use of neural networks in NLP tasks, which falls under the scope of this sub-category.
